p.d: This of course rhymes with "Heart" which is Lucy's surname and I must always do a rhyming slogan for every girl; do not enquire why, it is just so! Anyway, Lucy passed her casting with flying colours and was more than eager for Lara to take on the chore of holding the camcorder, so we could get on with the business of some serious screwing. As you can see, Lucy left on her sheer stockings and high heels during our second bout and as a result drove me crazy. What is it about stockings that drives men mad?
